title: Sony Multi Keygen
description:
This is a multi-keygen that will work with any Sony product.

To use just download a trial off of sony's product website.
Install and when it asks for serial open keygen and select the product you're trying to get.
If the product on the keygen says patch you will need to go to C:Program Files and select it. to run the patch.
REMEMBER..You will probably have to click Generate a couple times to get a working one.

PLEASE SEED! thanks
